                <dd class="terms-list__description">Pitch Hero Limited ("<strong>We</strong>", "<strong>Us</strong>" and "<strong>Our</strong>") takes the privacy rights of users of the PITCHERO.COM platform and website ("<strong>Website</strong>") seriously.</dd>
                <dt class="terms-list__term">1.2</dt>
                <dd class="terms-list__description">This privacy policy explains to you how certain information about you may be processed. By using the PITCHERO.COM platform, you expressly consent to the use of Your Data in accordance with this privacy policy.</dd>
                <dt class="terms-list__term">1.3</dt>
                <dd class="terms-list__description">For the purposes of the Data Protection Act 1998, the data controller is Pitch Hero Limited ("Pitch Hero") of Unit 8, Centre 27 Business Park, Bankwood Way, Birstall, Leeds, United Kingdom.</dd>
            </dl>
        </dd>
    </dl>


