            <dl class="c-terms-list">
                <dt class="terms-list__term">2.1</dt>
                <dd class="terms-list__description">For the purposes of this privacy policy, "Your Data" means any information about you from which You are personally identifiable, including without limitation your name, address, email address or telephone number (and where applicable, your login name and password) and other information from which you can be identified and which you may disclose to Us or otherwise via Pitch Hero at any time.</dd>
                <dt class="terms-list__term">2.2</dt>
                <dd class="terms-list__description">Please note that any video, image, or other content posted by you or at the direction of other users onto the Website becomes published content and is not considered personally identifiable information subject to this privacy policy.</dd>
            </dl>
        </dd>
    </dl>


    <dl class="c-terms-list">
