                        <dd class="terms-list__description">asking you to participate in market research, for example surveys about topical issues, conducted by Us or trusted partners or reputable third parties. We will always try to tell you before you participate in a survey how any information you provide in the survey will be used.</dd>
                    </dl>
                </dd>
                <dt class="terms-list__term">4.3</dt>
                <dd class="terms-list__description">
